OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers appoint Rob
OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FRob Edwards has been appointed as the
OL,7,Fnew Wolverhampton Wanderers' head
OL,8,Fcoach.
OL,10,FThis comes after the club sacked head
OL,11,Fcoach Vitor Pereira on November 2nd,
OL,12,Fafter a string of poor results in the
OL,13,FPremier League.
OL,15,FEdwards will be talking over the club
OL,16,Fas it sits at the bottom of the table
OL,17,Fwith just two points and no wins this
OL,18,Fseason.
