OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers appoint Rob
OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FWolverhampton Wanderers were given
OL,7,Fpermission to speak with Edwards after
OL,8,Fa compensation fee between #3-4
OL,9,Fmillion was accepted by Middlesbrough.
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough initially turned down
OL,12,FWolves' approach, having only
OL,13,Finstalled Edwards as their manager in
OL,14,FJune on a three-year deal following
OL,15,Fthe dismissal of Michael Carrick.
OL,17,FBut, the Sky Bet Championship club
OL,18,Fannounced last Saturday that they had
OL,19,Freluctantly agreed terms with Wolves,
OL,20,Fwhile Edwards did not take charge of
OL,21,Ftheir home win against Birmingham.
