OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FWithin a year, he was working under
OL,7,FKenny Jackett as first-team coach, and
OL,8,Fin October 2016 took charge of two
OL,9,Ffirst-team matches on an interim
OL,10,Fbasis, following Walter Zenga's time
OL,11,Fat Molineux.
OL,13,FAfter a first taste of senior
OL,14,Fmanagement with AFC Telford United,
OL,15,FEdwards returned to Wolves once more
OL,16,Fas under-23 head coach and won a first
OL,17,Fpromotion to the highest level of
OL,18,Fyouth football for the club.
