OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FTime coaching within the Football
OL,7,FAssociation followed, as did a first
OL,8,Fpiece of silverware in senior
OL,9,Fmanagement with Forest Green, having
OL,10,Fwon the League Two title in 2022,
OL,11,Fbefore a brief stint with Watford.
OL,13,FFormer Wolves defender Edwards made
OL,14,Fover 100 appearances during his time
OL,15,Fthere as a player from 2004 to 2008
OL,16,Fand held various coaching roles at
OL,17,FMolineux before taking charge of
OL,18,FForest Green in 2021.
