OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers appoint Rob
OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FHe led Luton to the Premier League in
OL,7,F2023 and has also had a spell in
OL,8,Fcharge at Watford, while Boro have
OL,9,Fmounted a promotion challenge this
OL,10,Fseason and currently sit second in the
OL,11,FChampionship.
OL,13,FWolverhampton Wanderers, Executive
OL,14,FChairman Jeff Shi said: "I know Rob
OL,15,Fvery well and I have seen his growth
OL,16,Fin different jobs. He's a very good
OL,17,Fperson, he knows the club very well,
OL,18,Fhe knows the city, the fans and he is
OL,19,Fvery talented.
