OL,6,F"When he was a youth coach here, he
OL,7,Fshowed his tactical awareness, but
OL,8,Fafter he took first-team jobs, he
OL,9,Fstarted to grow his own identity,
OL,10,Fcharacter and leadership.
OL,12,F"We need to refresh the whole club
OL,13,Fwith a new coach's philosophy,
OL,14,Fbringing his own identity and ideas,
OL,15,Fand we can build on that. We are at a
OL,16,Fnew chapter for the club and Rob will
OL,17,Fbe a key piece of that."
