OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers appoint Rob
OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FWolves parted company with Vitor
OL,7,FPereira following a run of eight
OL,8,Fdefeats from their opening 10 games
OL,9,Fthis season and discussed the vacancy
OL,10,Fwith their former boss Gary O'Neil,
OL,11,Fwho later withdrew from the process.
OL,13,FAfter that decision was made,
OL,14,FExecutive Chairman Jeff Shi said:
OL,15,F"Vitor and his team worked tirelessly
OL,16,Ffor Wolves and helped guide us through
OL,17,Fa challenging period last season, for
OL,18,Fwhich we are grateful.
