OL,6,F"Unfortunately, the start to this
OL,7,Fseason has been a disappointment and,
OL,8,Fdespite our strong desire to give the
OL,9,Fhead coach time and matches to find an
OL,10,Fimprovement, we have reached a point
OL,11,Fwhere we must make a change.
OL,13,F"We thank Vitor and his staff for
OL,14,Ftheir efforts and wish them the very
OL,15,Fbest for the future."
OL,17,FPereira was announced as head coach
OL,18,Fback in December last year after
OL,19,Fdeparting Saudi Pro League club Al
OL,20,FShabab.
