OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers appoint Rob
OL,4,CEdwards as their new head coach
OL,6,FEdwards will be joined at the club by
OL,7,FHarry Watling, who takes on the role
OL,8,Fof assistant head coach.
OL,10,FAfter nine years in academy football,
OL,11,FWatling gained managerial experience
OL,12,Fwith Hartford Athletic in the US and
OL,13,FEbbsfleet United last year, before
OL,14,Fjoining Edwards' team at Middlesbrough.
OL,16,FThe club has said more backroom staff
OL,17,Fwill be confirmed in the near future.
